('790eb021-00ad-4e63-8355-4b4f7e1113cc', 'title.egyptian_colloquial', 'CRITICAL: When generating content in Arabic, you MUST use Egyptian Colloquial Arabic (المصرية العامية). Do NOT use Modern Standard Arabic (الفصحى) or any other Arabic dialect. Use natural, conversational Egyptian Arabic that is commonly spoken in Egypt. Examples: use "عايز" instead of "يريد", "عندي" instead of "لدي", "إيه" instead of "ماذا", "عشان" instead of "لأن", "في" instead of "يوجد", etc.', 'case', null, 2, 1, true, '{"category":"title","type":"restriction"}', '2026-01-03 09:33:45+02', '2026-01-03 09:33:45+02', null, null, 'EN'),
